# ERROR TIPS

### Inventory full when harvesting
- Ensure that the agent has enough space in its inventory before attempting to harvest items.

### Could not extract item due to no valid entity
- Ensure that there is a valid entity at the target location that contains the item to be extracted. The agent is trying to extract from (0,0) which is probably empty.
